item.title: Mentored Sprint
item.description: Mentored Sprint is a beginner-friendly sprint that encourages new contributors to open source. During the sprints, project leaders will be able to help you pick an issue, set up your development environment, and show you the contribution workflow. You may also be encouraged to pair up with someone to contribute together.
